This easy to follow Latin-inspired dance fitness class will sculpt and tone your body with non-stop, calorie burning, and high-energy fun! This class is great for all and brings together movement and music for an exciting workout! No dance experience required.

Discover varying terrains while riding along to a unique playlist. Each instructor brings a different style to their class to give you a different challenge each ride. Cycle Fit is meant to make you sweat, increase your heart rate and have fun! Perfect for new and advanced riders.

Explore a gentle, yet powerful series of postures and breathing techniques that promote physical strength, flexibility, and mental clarity.Whether you are a beginner or an experienced practitioner,HathaYoga offers a balanced approach to cultivate inner peace, enhance mindfulness, and restore harmony to your being. Join us and experience the transformative benefits ofHathaYoga for overall well-being and vitality.

Inspired by elements of ballet, yoga, and Pilates, this class focuses on low-impact, high-intensity movements designed to strengthen your body and give you long lean muscles. Youll use low-weight and high repetitions. No dance experience required.

Challenge yourself with this great cardio conditioning class! Instructors will lead you through a variety of challenging rides including hills, sprints and team riding all set to great motivating music. Suitable for all levels of riders.

This class emphasizes precise movements to activate, isolate, and stabilize core muscles. This class is great for improving posture, flexibility, balance and strength, to help you stay strong throughout your workweek. The class is a mixture of beginner and intermediate exercises and options will be given for all levels.

This workout uses resistance training with high repetitions to activate fast twitch muscle fibers. You will grow strong, lean muscle mass and enhance your athleticism. The calorie burn wont just stop after the class is over - your lean muscle fibers will keep you burning calories for long after youve left!
